oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Holbrook Normal College, Fountain City, TN
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: J.E. Story, Knoxville, TN
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Students of Holbrook Normal College, Fountain City, TN. Posed outside brick building. Ca. 1890s. The building was later sold to the Tennessee Baptist Association and burned in the early 1900s. The location is the present site of Gresham Middle School.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Universities & colleges; Group portraits;
